	%       ``org.eclipse.cdt'', then click on the .project file
	%\item  Under ``New tags found in the selected files'', click on the Deselect
	%       All button, then check cdt\_6\_0 in the list above it
	%\item	 Click Add Checked Tags
	%\item	 Click OK
